psalm.text:
[[Ps 89,20]]Once you spoke in vision;
to your faithful ones you said: 
“On a champion I have placed a crown;
over the people I have set a youth.”

[[Ps 89,21]]I have chosen David, my servant; 
with my holy oil I have anointed him.
[[Ps 89,22]]That my hand will be with him; 
and that my arm will make him strong.

[[Ps 89,25]]My loyalty and love will be with him; 
through my name his horn will be exalted.
[[Ps 89,26]]I will set his hand upon the sea,
his right hand upon the rivers.
